:"3c578ac0139a1801dc1740a7f94acb2be7ae2496","tid":907520,"uid":19485,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"6a3ba4f0e7941a256f38e96963654065d22df955","tid":907520,"uid":167536,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T01:08:21.000Z","msg":"之前去過S21 參觀，慘絕人寰到夜晚訓唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T01:20:20.000Z","msg":"參觀過唔同地方既監獄<br />\n呢個暫時為止係最震撼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n行過堆相中間好似好多眼望住你咁, 地下又有大大小小乾咗既血跡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇到一半頂唔順中途要出中庭抖抖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n未去波蘭集中營, 唔知S21難頂啲定波蘭個難頂啲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T02:41:48.000Z","msg":"波蘭果個我都去過，唔知係咪去之前已經睇過好多相，所以無咁震撼。S21 係恐怖好多，睇到喊"},{"pid":"2219e4ba2fefc3b751fd5ff3e34d33158472e606","tid":907520,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T02:44:51.000Z","msg":"細細間學校屠左過百萬人"},{"pid":"237a4502aced5641a363b3fef1185f790b766134","tid":907520,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4da37642c05bed6f6d59c6a50ce527b8629c7e1a","tid":907520,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T01:23:50.000Z","msg":"共產黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T02:59:23.000Z","msg":"最後比馬共KO<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ac95cb7f5aaffd3dc9816d8598aa7bd612c5a34","tid":907520,"uid":202348,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T03:08:26.000Z","msg":"呢啲弱智南亞種又矮又窮又無腦，種族滅絕對地球環境同人文進步都係一件好事"},{"pid":"330253aa46c4d35c29a79f0a95810f9e4f5e53d6","tid":907520,"uid":19552,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"0ac95cb7f5aaffd3dc9816d8598aa7bd612c5a34","tid":907520,"uid":202348,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T03:08:26.000Z","msg":"呢啲弱智南亞種又矮又窮又無腦，種族滅絕